review_blob: Bottle, nice dark brown color, well balanced flavor and aroma, wonderful beer, its not imported in Louisiana so I am out of luck
Great flavor and good aroma.  Full hop flavor and a wonderful finish.  Golden color and light colored head that lasts longer than expected.
Wonderful aroma of strong fruits.  Flavor covers up the strong alcohol content.  Amazing!

Disappointing fruit beer in a bottle.  Compared to the other specialties that I have had this is one of the weakest taste wise.  It has a very nice appearance but not enough to make me want to buy it again.
I had this on draught, little or no aroma but taste wasnt bad.  I would have this again but nothing special.  Crisp and refreshing but nothing to brag about.
Great beer with a small touch of alcohol in the aroma.  Just enough alcohol to warm the senses and a wonderful taste to match.
